  <entry>
    <title>tableau使用方法记录</title>
    <link href="/2024/07/15/tableau-study/"/>
    <url>/2024/07/15/tableau-study/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>Data Workflow</h1><p>数据平台<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>⇒</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Rightarrow</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.3669em;"></span><span class="mrel">⇒</span></span></span></span>数据存储<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>⇒</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Rightarrow</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.3669em;"></span><span class="mrel">⇒</span></span></span></span>数据获取<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>⇒</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Rightarrow</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.3669em;"></span><span class="mrel">⇒</span></span></span></span>数据分析与处理<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>⇒</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Rightarrow</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.3669em;"></span><span class="mrel">⇒</span></span></span></span>数据可视化<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>⇒</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Rightarrow</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.3669em;"></span><span class="mrel">⇒</span></span></span></span>理解数据，得出结论</p><h1>Data Profiling</h1><p>examing &amp; analyzing &amp; reviewing &amp; summarizing</p><ul><li><p>Data Overview</p><ul><li>Data Domain &amp; Description</li><li>Data Schema</li><li>Data Type</li><li>Data Range</li><li>Data Distribution</li></ul></li><li><p>Data Quality</p><ul><li>Missing Data</li><li>Abnormal Data</li><li>Over-bounding Data</li><li>Redundant Data：重复填写</li><li>Inconsistent Data : 同一个东西不同的说法不应分在不同类</li></ul></li></ul><h1>Data Wrangling</h1><p>cleaning &amp; transforming</p><ul><li>Data Transformations<ul><li>Sort : ascending , descending</li><li>Filter : math <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>≤</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\leq</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7719em;vertical-align:-0.136em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span></span></span></span> 80</li><li>Distinct</li><li>Sllice</li><li>Extract</li><li>Mutate</li><li>Replace</li><li>Split</li><li>Merge</li><li>Aggregate</li><li>Reshape</li><li>Join : Inner join , right join , left join , full join （区别在于是否保留差异项以及保留哪张表的差异部分）</li></ul></li></ul><h1>Introduction : Tableau</h1>]]></content>
    
    
